---
const personalImageAlt = "Kevin Simorangkir";
const defaultImage = "/VINS.png";
const seventeeneightImage = "/VINSSS.png";
---

<article class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-8 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 md:flex-row seventeen-eight-profile">
  <div
    class="[&>p]:mb-4 [&>p>strong]:text-yellow-500 dark:[&>p>strong]:text-yellow-100 [&>p>strong]:font-normal [&>p>strong]:font-mono text-pretty order-2 md:order-1"
  >
    <p>
      My name is Kevin Simorangkir, and I began learning programming in high school, driven by my interest in creating computer games and mobile applications.  I have contributed to several communities/companies, producing projects such as <strong
        >REFORA ITERA, Harvesty, SIPAD, and other feed designs.</strong
      >
    </p>

    <p>
      These include
      <strong>Telkom Witel Lampung, Telkom Indonesia, Yayasan Media Selaras, Baparekraf Digital Talent.</strong
      > Throughout my contributions, I have enjoyed each experience and strive to improve and continue growing in the future.
    </p>
  </div>

  <img width="200" height="200" 
       src={defaultImage} 
       alt={personalImageAlt} 
       class="order-1 object-cover w-64 h-full p-1 md:order-2 rotate-3 lg:p-2 lg:w-64 aspect-square rounded-2xl bg-black/20 dark:bg-yellow-500/5 ring-1 ring-black/70 dark:ring-white/20 profile-image"
       style="object-position: 50% 50%">
</article>

<style is:global>
  /* Tema SeventeenEight khusus profile */
  html.seventeen-eight .seventeen-eight-profile,
  html.seventeen-eight .seventeen-eight-profile * {
    color: #1B602F !important; /* semua teks hijau */
  }

  /* strong yang sebelumnya kuning menjadi biru */
  html.seventeen-eight .seventeen-eight-profile strong {
    color: #000072 !important;
  }

  /* Ganti gambar untuk tema SeventeenEight */
  html.seventeen-eight .seventeen-eight-profile .profile-image {
    content: url('/VINSSS.png') !important;
  }
</style>
